{"tid":2170282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中華民國國防部：戰到一兵一卒，永遠守護台灣","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T16:09:28.000Z","uid":226955,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8cda72fe8ad4889dadee9573ade453413d5d1808","tid":2170282,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQqSCZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQqSCZ8.jpg&h=43dd6bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共對台文攻武嚇施壓加大，今天是金門823炮戰62周年紀念日，台國防部發佈「枕戈待旦，同島一命」影片，強調面對中共的軍事威脅，台軍「能戰、敢戰、戰到一兵一卒」，永遠守護台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VGiyyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VGiyyA.jpg&h=0fad99c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8jj2rW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8jj2rW.jpg&h=35bdb09a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgkbTyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgkbTyB.jpg&h=841edd92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全長75秒的影片除提及國軍護國具有歷史傳承使命，更細數共軍今年以來海空演訓、軍機越台海中線、宣稱在台海南北兩端軍演，都嚴重影響區域安全和台海穩定，「國軍有信心，也有能力，迫使敵人犯台失敗」。<br />\n<br />\n台國防部表示，國軍守護中華民國具有歷史傳承使命，當年將士們用生命在戰火威脅下保衛國家，台人應共同珍惜這份得來不易的和平成果。他們又表示，歷史證明，和平不能寄望於敵人的善意，安全必須建立在自己有實力。自年初以來，中共即不斷在台灣周邊海、空域進行演訓，共機甚至惡意挑釁，跨越海峽中線，其侵門踏戶之舉，已令國人深惡痛絕；近期更宣稱在海峽南北兩端接連進行軍演，不論是對區域安全或是臺海的穩定，都已經造成嚴重影響。因應當前中共軍事威脅，國軍本「不挑釁、不示弱」的原則，強化各項戰備整備，以達到「勿恃敵之不來，恃吾有以待之」目標。<br />\n<br />\n台國防部進一步表示，台軍近年來在建軍備戰，以及災害救援上的努力，讓國人有目共睹。尤其從歷次的實兵演訓、漢光演習中，官兵以「從嚴、從難、從實」的高標準進行訓練，證明國軍能戰、敢戰、善戰，永遠守護台灣。他們強調，國軍就是一支「平時能救災，戰時能作戰」的鋼鐵勁旅，而戰力的發揚，關鍵並不在時間的長短，憑藉的是守護自由民主的決心。國軍有信心，也有能力，迫使敵人犯台失敗，即使戰到最後一兵一卒，也絕不會讓敵人越雷池一步！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200823/RCW44SIPF5GVTOAWA5MKU6SF4M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200823%2FRCW44SIPF5GVTOAWA5MKU6SF4M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=6b33e647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200823%2FRCW44SIPF5GVTOAWA5MKU6SF4M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=497c3043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200823/RCW44SIPF5GVTOAWA5MKU6SF4M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"33b32ff2530428dc7aaf0b7200dca93ffc5f0867","tid":2170282,"uid":8014,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"要求唔高，能戰到沖繩美軍到台就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa97211c5cf9998151bb7824b8a9b821f853b04","tid":2170282,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"33b32ff2530428dc7aaf0b7200dca93ffc5f0867","tid":2170282,"uid":8014,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"要求唔高，能戰到沖繩美軍到台就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"只需一個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d4db79bf70e885c3ef763f3b83501b5e402719","tid":2170282,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"daa97211c5cf9998151bb7824b8a9b821f853b04","tid":2170282,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"33b32ff2530428dc7aaf0b7200dca93ffc5f0867","tid":2170282,"uid":8014,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"要求唔高，能戰到沖繩美軍到台就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"